description: Seinfeld Guru is a fun trivia skill that gives users ability to test their knowledge about the TV show. Players can see what they really remember about Jerry, George, Elaine, Kramer, and the rest of the gang by answering multiple choice questions. Great for parties or solo play.
name: My First Trivia Skill
shortDescription: Are you a fan of Seinfeld? Then enable Seinfeld Guru and see how much you really know about the hilarious sitcom from the '90s!
